  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Protect 50,000 Girls from Child Marriage in Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Protect 50,000 Girls from Child, Early and Forced Marriage in Northern Ghana by providing school materials, facilitators to in/out-of-school Girl-Only SafeSpaces, community-based non-formal education in reproductive health, democracy, human rights to child and out of school brides, one-on-one counseling, rehabilitation, a best in/out-class life skills curriculum for victims of sexual abuse as well as Community Conversations on child/early marriage and harmful traditional practices in Ghana.</narrative>
  </description>
